<i>adjective</i>: 우스꽝스럽다 [우스꽝스럽따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>우스꽝스럽다 [우스꽝스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. ridiculous; laughable; comical</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동, 모습 등이 보통과 달라 우습다.</dd><br>
<dd>Funny because one's remarks, behavior, appearance, etc., are not ordinary.</dd><br>
<dd>2. ludicrous; absurd; nonsensical</dd><br>
<dd>매우 못나서 우스운 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Somewhat funny because something or someone is very foolish.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>